      "message": "I\u0027ve refactored this code (semantically constructX509 was constructing PEM and not X509) and re-used it and key generation in tests.\n\nAs testing, apart from unit testing, I deployed the image with this change to QEMU and checked generated server SSL cert with `openssl s_client -connect 127.0.0.1 8443` and made sure it\u0027s the same (has same properties, validity dates were obviously different) as the one generated without this change.",
